# MCP Tools First

When looking up documentation, APIs, or external information for this project:

1. **Use MCP tools first** — check enabled MCP servers (e.g. Astro docs, Cloudflare docs, GitHub) before any other lookup method.
2. **Fall back only when MCP cannot help** — use `WebFetch` or `WebSearch` only if no relevant MCP tool exists or MCP calls fail to answer the question.
3. **Read MCP tool schemas** — list and read tool descriptors in the MCP filesystem before calling tools.

Do not skip MCP and go straight to web search when an applicable MCP server is available.
